<p style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="background-color: transparent;">In February 2019, Software&nbsp;</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;">Passport user accounts were migrated to Access Manager as part of the separation from HPE.&nbsp; However, ITOM Marketplace APIs such as the ones used in HCM/CSA Content Store were not able to make this migration and have continued to use Software Passport Credentials to authenticate.&nbsp;ITOM Marketplace Team announced the end of authentication using Software Passport by August&nbsp;</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">30th</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 12px;">&nbsp;</span><span style="background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt;">2019.&nbsp; This means, HCM/CSA Conent Store will no longer be able to authenticate to ITOM Marketplace using the Software Passport Credentials starting September 1st 2019.</span></p><div><h2 style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: MetricHPE; margin-top: 22.5pt; text-transform: none; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Access Manager Account Creation</h2></div><div><p style="margin: 7.5pt 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">To update your credentials to Access Manager in Content Store, first create an&nbsp;<a href="https://www.microfocus.com/selfreg/jsp/createAccount.jsp"><span style="color: rgb(59, 115, 175);">Access Manager account here</span></a>&nbsp;if you do not have one. If you access entitled software, you should also configure your entitlements and contracts in the&nbsp;<a href="https://softwaresupport.softwaregrp.com/group/softwaresupport/settings?lang=en&amp;cc=us&amp;hpappid=206728_SSO_PRO"><span style="color: rgb(59, 115, 175);">My entitlements section here</span></a>&nbsp;in MySupport.&nbsp; You can go to the&nbsp;<a href="https://marketplace.microfocus.com/login?returnUrl=/itom"><span style="color: rgb(59, 115, 175);">Marketplace login page here</span></a>&nbsp;and login using Access Manager to test your account if needed.<o:p></o:p></span></p><h2 style="margin-top: 22.5pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">HCM/CSA Content Store Configuration Steps</h2></div><div><p style="margin: 7.5pt 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">To update Content Store settings in HCM/CSA:</span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 21pt; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">1.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">In the HCM/CSA Console Settings navigation frame, select&nbsp;Content Store.</span></p><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 21pt; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">2.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">Provide or update the following information, under Micro Focus Software Password Credentials :<o:p></o:p></span></p><table class="MsoNormalTable" border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" style="width: 438.889px; margin-left: 21pt;"><thead><tr><td valign="top" style="background: rgb(240, 240, 240); padding: 5.25pt 11.25pt 5.25pt 7.5pt; border-width: 1pt; border-left-style: solid; border-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-image: initial;"><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-weight: 700;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">Item</span></span><span style="font-weight: 700;"><span style="font-size: 12pt; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><o:p></o:p></span></span></p></td><td valign="top" style="background: rgb(240, 240, 240); padding: 5.25pt 11.25pt 5.25pt 7.5pt; border-top-width: 1pt; border-top-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-image: initial; border-left: none;"><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-weight: 700;"><span style="color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">Description<o:p></o:p></span></span></p></td></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td valign="top" style="padding: 5.25pt 7.5pt; border-top: none; border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-left: 1pt solid rgb(221, 221, 221); border-image: initial;"><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">User Name<o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td valign="top" style="padding: 5.25pt 7.5pt; border-top: none; border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-left: none;"><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt;"><span style="font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 9pt; letter-spacing: 0.2px; background-color: transparent;">The Micro Focus Access Manager account username.</span><br></p></td></tr><tr><td valign="top" style="padding: 5.25pt 7.5pt; border-top: none; border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-left: 1pt solid rgb(221, 221, 221); border-image: initial;"><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">Password<o:p></o:p></span></p></td><td valign="top" style="padding: 5.25pt 7.5pt; border-top: none; border-right-width: 1pt; border-right-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-bottom-width: 1pt; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); border-left: none;"><p class="MsoNormal"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;">The password for the Access Manager username<o:p></o:p></span></p></td></tr></tbody></table><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 21pt; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">3.<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">Click&nbsp;Validate.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin: 7.5pt 0in 0.0001pt 21pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">The validations pass/fail message appears at the top of the window.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin: 7.5pt 0in 0.0001pt 21pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">Validation passed&nbsp;- the settings are all valid and the Content Store will display the ITOM Marketplace capsule tiles.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin: 7.5pt 0in 0.0001pt 21pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">Validation failed&nbsp;- one or more settings are not valid and the Content Store remains disabled for ITOM Marketplace capsules.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 21pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">If the validation fails, check the following:<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 39pt; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">·<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">You have access to the internet through the proxy information you provided.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 39pt; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">·<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">Your Access Manager credentials are correct.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p style="margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 21pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"></p><p class="MsoNormal" style="margin-left: 39pt; text-indent: -0.25in; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 10pt; font-family: Symbol; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">·<span style="font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">You have permission to access the&nbsp;<span class="productnamescsa">CSA/HCM&nbsp;</span>product page on the&nbsp;<span class="csavariablesitom">ITOM Marketplace</span>.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p></p><p style="margin: 7.5pt 0in 0.0001pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;"><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);">4.&nbsp; &nbsp;Click&nbsp;Save&nbsp;when the configuration is validated to enable the Content Store tile.</span><span style="font-size: 9pt; font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><br></span></p><h2 style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: MetricHPE; margin-top: 22.5pt; text-transform: none; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;">Upgrade Scenario</h2></div><p style="font-size: 16px;">All the HCM users(prior to 2019.11) and CSA users(prior to 4.99) who are upgrading to 2019.11+ and 4.99+ respectively, needs to perform the above&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: 700;">Steps&nbsp;</span>before performing their product upgrades for seamless Content Store experience.</p>